{"id":177130,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/中国正在消失的老行业/","date":"2011-09-04T14:30:03Z","modified":"2011-09-04T14:30:03Z","title":"中国正在消失的老行业","content":"<p><p>捏面人、钉称、吹糖技艺、铜匠、扯脸、磨剪子、爆米花、修钢笔、修钟表、蒲编工艺、麦秸编织、框裱、补锅……</p>\n<p>有多少行业曾经辉煌一时，有多少行业曾伴我在成长的过程中走过，有多少行业正在逐步地消逝，有多少行业已经淡出我们的视线？</p>\n<p>民族的才是世界的，这些民俗文化只留下这一张张的照片，成为记忆当中最深处的怀念。向还在从事这些活动的普通劳动者致敬，你们是最伟大的艺术家。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/ikQzT6itmdq36.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/iCML23FozSyjY.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/i5MQ0YHCi645k.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/ioiVdWRARTDUd.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/iyIZCM6Ww4mWI.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/ibvwPNcASIXSce.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/iboosK61YAIAZs.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/ibkllBCmA1igL5.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/ibpleUC9pC32tJ.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/iAARCmEfyYtG1.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/ihJVORTYrntJo.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/ife5KdhMKMOeR.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/ijtQsPmFMmgfQ.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/iCRiQXcXyEYl1.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/ibz0Ucr1diUFvY.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/ibbr3IhcIwq2uf.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/iUC5mSQq7JKCz.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/ibcofyE5a41m1l.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/i0xiw7CoHjuYR.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/iDDYeYexE3zc6.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/iboHs6RBq5X2OQ.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/ibyaNch05SMQUX.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/iruojo3BYGwOJ.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.min.us/isX3808sMKWuw.jpg\" /></p>\n